  "bio_raw": "Dr. Shahana has more than twelve years teaching experience, leading and managing projects on renewable energy, experienced in research and development with a demonstrated history of working in the renewable energy, development sector and renowned academic institutions in Australia and Bangladesh. She is skilled in handling sustainable development projects, renewable energy, climate change and environment, agriculture and rural development. She is currently teaching sustainable development courses under General Education Department.",
